# Mext

Mext is an prompt template extension for LLM (large language model).

## Syntax

### if

Template:
```mext
{@import "if.yaml"}

{@if true}
This will be shown.
{@endif}

{@if not empty var}
{var}
{@endif}
```

Given params:
```json
{
  "var": "Text from variable."
}
```

Produce:
```markdown
This will be shown.

Text from variable.
```
### for

Template:
```mext
{@import "for.yaml"}

## Array
{@for item in arr}
- name: {item[name]}
  content: {item[content]}
{@endfor}

## Dictionary
{@for item in dict.items}
- key: {item[0]}
  val: {item[1]}
{@endfor}
```

Given params:
```json
{
  "arr": [
    {
      "name": "Item 1",
      "content": "Content 1"
    },
    {
      "name": "Item 2",
      "content": "Content 2"
    }
  ],
  "dict": {
    "key1": "Value 1",
    "key2": "Value 2"
  }
}
```

Produce:
```markdown
## Array
- name: Item 1
  content: Content 1
- name: Item 2
  content: Content 2

## Dictionary
- key: key1
  val: Value 1
- key: key2
  val: Value 2
```